{"tid":932697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國女教師強行為學生剪髮 面臨最高三年半監禁","createTime":"2018-12-08T03:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T03:29:44.000Z","uid":136994,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c923106b38f1682bdc600ea6c5be80a1c8a245f","tid":932697,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T03:26:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181208/59006042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59006042&d=OSJohsYyHL5iu1o8J2i1JwKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=b00e08a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F59006042&h=8bcca835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181208/59006042</a><br />\n<br />\n美國加州一名中學女教師，因強行為一名男學生剪頭髮，被控數項殘酷對待兒童和毆打罪。<br />\n<br />\n52歲教師吉斯辛格(Margaret Gieszinger)日前強行為一名高中學生剪髮，片段之後被上載到社交網站。警方周三把她拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n根據片段，任教科學和化學科的吉斯辛格，一邊唱著美國國歌，一邊為該名學生剪頭髮，再大動作把剪下的頭髮扔到身後。圖萊里縣(Tulare)檢察廳說，若全部6項罪名均成立，吉斯辛格可被判監3年半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔止香港班「訓導主任」喺美國要坐幾年監呢？"},{"pid":"557c8157a81dcbfd789337c0469c42eaf5ce64ea","tid":932697,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T03:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}